[As at least one of the 2 cases in Dubasari has died I think we can presume that this report refers to livestock cases, and as they quote "mad cow" probably bovine.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Moldova can be seen at http://healthmap.org/r/7pn0. For the location of Dubasari and Transnistria in a map of Moldova, go to http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/commonwealth/moldova_pol01.jpg; Dubasari Province is currently under the administration of the breakaway government of the Moldovan Republic of Transnistria. - Mod.MHJ]
